<Layout title="Stats" description="What each stat actually does for mid-game players in Last War: Survival and stat priority order.">
  <h1>Stats</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-[#8a96b0]">Not all stats are equal. Here’s what actually moves the needle for new and mid-game players.</p>

  <h2>Priority Order (Mid-Game)</h2>
  <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 space-y-1">
    <li><strong>Attack / Lethality</strong> — Your damage output</li>
    <li><strong>Defense / HP</strong> — Survivability (especially frontline)</li>
    <li><strong>March Size</strong> — More troops = more power in almost every mode</li>
    <li><strong>Troop Load</strong> — Critical for gathering and resource events</li>
    <li>Secondary stats (accuracy, dodge, etc.) become more relevant later</li>
  </ol>
</Layout>